{"id":"64a45829-a03e-4f3a-a21d-d23b4e15cfd9","title":"1556/08/01: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"207e7299-f9a1-4c2b-8161-0f1948551611","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, August 1st, 1556.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c5e50abd-0a71-4373-ac5c-b55e06d48959","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"62b32276-f594-4c29-850e-1ca965987476","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0a06524f-df45-422c-9f0b-f7cdec538cf7","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":26,"value":"00c7a229-4c74-4ab6-9926-d85389cb79df","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"aa36f97b-1a49-4bb9-a723-6723fcf5c37c","type":"style/superscript","start":19,"end":20,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"1b453957-7214-40e1-bcc3-86121a6b0b1a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6d1fc8cd-69b5-4240-9e76-32436feb74ee","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f8fe82ba-136a-487a-a519-2747293b7d43","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"565710ad-2c83-469a-8c27-d470364cfed0","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"22654a75-d101-4e05-815a-8d9c584960ac","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2124d05d-9f7e-4373-b3d8-c34a533c411c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f611ae9e-0990-444c-9ad5-d6f22eccaea1","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"807ab45e-3d04-46b7-92b2-fb01e4e94fd0","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0Thy haste [with regard to Cepperello\u0027s farm] hast cost me at least fifty crowns more than it need have done; but what grieves me most is that thou shouldst have more regard for a piece of land than for what I say. Thou knowest well what I said\u00A0to thee: thou wert to pretend that I did not want the land, and to make them come to us and beg us to buy. But thou, so soon as thou hadst returned to\u00A0Florence, set the agents to negotiate for it with the\u00A0greatest eagerness. However, since it is done take\u00A0care of thy health so that thou mayst live to enjoy it.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"ab2b2148-63c4-458d-a713-97afc84e5608","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"75a8b637-1b8d-472e-bccc-bd407424cb33","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"461f3c28-b41f-4837-bba5-4d75358708fc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":14,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b44869e6-6017-4e3b-bee1-3031e36a018c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":47,"value":"7560bbfa-96f9-4872-9774-2cdfb0f93924","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e6e50e68-8657-4496-9ae3-fd7072424a70","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":51,"end":54,"value":"f3cc72f0-7f61-4e8d-9743-ab0b6296ff48","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ce641980-57ef-40d0-b844-2c7480a793ba","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":67,"end":68,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ccd0fac5-0485-48ff-846e-dfe2414918cc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":138,"end":139,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1bd1acf6-d090-4728-a6e5-